</code></pre> <p>Rule of Thumb: - The first parameter of <code>belongsTo()</code> or <code>hasMany()</code> MUST match your getter name - The first parameter MUST match the Salesforce relationship name you use in queries - For custom lookups, use <code>__r</code> suffix (e.g., <code>User__r</code>)</p>
